lead_paragraph: Wrapping up a stretch of four tough games in 10 days, No. 4 Maryland switched into survival mode late in a Big Ten matchup with No. 18 Purdue.

headline.print_headline: No. 4 Maryland Rallies for 72-61 Win Over No. 18 Purdue
